Cafe Mavoor at The Raviz Calicut is where you should be if you are craving for traditional flavours and textures of Mexican cuisine. Get a taste of the best in town tortillas, tapas, quesadillas, tacos or chimichangas at the vibrant  Chipotle Mexican food fair from 8th to 17th November 2019. Buen apetito!

Contact: Toll Free: 1800 4252 2220|Email: reservations@theraviz.com
Visit: www.theraviz.com
